Change history for TXT2RTF

        2009-12-03 - Version 1.12
                   - Update from Mario Robitaille
                     to report on non-zero returns
        2008-12-01 - Version 1.11
                   - use quotes for x2c strings
        2008-09-01 - 1.10 remove never executed "exit"s
        2008-08-28 - 1.09 msgid correction
                   - compiled exec - fix msgid problem
                   - uniform msgid
        06/27/08 - 1.08
                 - add options support ver  e.g. ver=txt2rtf(ver)
        11/13/07 - 1.08
                 - Updated for NLS by Hartmut
        11/12/07 - 1.07
                 - Add info on the changes for German language
        01/22/07 - 1.06
