        03/09/06 - 1.05 from Billy Smith
                 - Allow keyword options to over-ride CONFIG values
        02/24/06 - 1.04 from Billy Smith
                 - Added option to set line spacing /*wls*/
        01/26/06 - 1.03
                 - Correction for mach cc x'09'
                   thx to Robert Charlesworth
        01/19/06 - 1.02
                 - Correct + CC if overlay is shorter than the primary
                   record
        02/05/04 - 1.01
                 - Add local variable for default font
        02/04/04 - 1.00
                 - Change from version 0. to version 1.00
                 - Correct to properly display the font in Word
        01/24/04 - 0.16
